Package: bremla
Type: Package
Title: Bayesian Regression Modeling of Layered Archives
Version: 0.2.2
Author: Eirik Myrvoll-Nilsen
Maintainer: Eirik Myrvoll-Nilsen <eirikmn91@gmail.com>
Description: Performs efficient Bayesian regression modeling of layer-counted climate records. Default method of inference is integrated nested Laplace approximations (INLAs).
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Imports: INLA, numDeriv, Matrix, matrixStats, ggplot2, rlang
Depends: R (>= 3.5)
Additional_repositories: https://inla.inla-r-download.org/R/testing
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.1.2
